title: Deja Voodo - Swamp of Love - Too Cool To Live Too Smart to Die
description:
The classic Albums from Deja Voodoo - 
- Swamp of Love 
and 
- Too Cool to Live, Too Smart to Die

Impossible to find on the Internet, as these babies were never put on DVD, or any Digital medium. 

I&#039;ve ripped them from the original Vinyl, cleaned up the audio, and posted them here. FINALLY!  

Enjoy the Sludgeabilly goodness that was Deja Voodoo.   One of Canada&#039;s best alternative bands of all time.
